column1: Checking the compatibility of the "Link-uri Utile" menu with the Microsoft Edge browser
column27:
Verify that the menu mentioned in the summary appears exactly the same on the Microsoft Edge browser as when the end user interacts with the menu using the Google Chrome browser.

*Preconditions:*

* The end user has a personal computer with at least Windows 10 Home, with the Microsoft Edge browser installed on it, along with a set of peripherals and a monitor.
* The end user is on the home page of the website: [https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.|https://www.primariatechirghiol.ro.]

*Acceptance criteria:*

* The menu still does not pose any danger to the positioning of other elements in that area of ​​the website, being correctly placed.
* No other buttons or other elements unrelated to the menu appear within the menu.
* The buttons do not undergo changes that could cause defects following a change in viewing resolution.
* The buttons still redirect the end user to the expected websites.
